    "Businesses must invest in the right technology and talent to maximize AI's consumer experience benefits.",
    "This comprises identifying consumer pain points that AI-powered products can solve and studying the organization's best AI tools and platforms.",
    "Businesses should hire data scientists and AI professionals to successfully deploy and manage AI-driven personalization strategies.",
    "Companies should also build consumer data foundations.",
    "The more precise and relevant data a company possesses, the more effective its AIdriven personalization tactics will be."
